text: Miss Lee () is a 2019 South Korean television series starring Lee Hye-ri, Kim Sang-kyung, Uhm Hyun-kyung and Cha Seo-won. Created by Studio Dragon and produced by Logos Film, it aired on tvN from September 25 to November 14, 2019. ==Synopsis== The story of an ordinary employee named Lee Seon-sim who suddenly becomes the CEO of the company she works at. ==Cast== ===Main=== * Lee Hye-ri as Lee Seon-sim * Kim Sang-kyung as Yoo Jin-wook * Uhm Hyun-kyung as Koo Ji-na * Cha Seo-won as Park Do-joon ===Supporting=== * Baek Ji-won as Choi Yeong-ja * Jung Hee-tae as Hwang Ji-sang * Jung Soo-young as Lee Sun-shin * Kim Eung-soo as Oh Man-bok * Kim Hyung-mook as Moon Hyeong-seok * Lee Hwa- ryong as Song Young-hoon ==Viewership== {| class="wikitable" style="text- align:center;max-width:450px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; border: none;" |- |+ Average TV viewership ratings |- !
